  "summary": "WordPress < 7.0.2 - Facilitated SQL Injection via author__not_in in WP_Query",
  "details": "WordPress 6.8.x before 6.8.6, 6.9.x before 6.9.5, and 7.0.x before 7.0.2 does not properly sanitise the author__not_in parameter of WP_Query, which could allow SQL Injection when a plugin or theme passes untrusted input to the parameter.",
